\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"15-year-old schoolgirl Enda Fofana\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"a free ticket\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Games\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It never materialised.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The teenager lives in Seine-Saint-Denis, a gritty, racially mixed suburb reaching north-east away from the capital, where the government and local mayors hope investment in new housing, sports facilities, metro lines and cycle lanes will leave a lasting legacy of urban and economic renewal.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 718, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The teenager\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"a gritty, racially mixed suburb\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"north-east\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"local mayors\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"new housing\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"sports facilities\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"metro lines\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"cycle lanes\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"a lasting legacy\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"urban and economic renewal\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games' organisers pledged that Seine-Saint-Denis would be a pulsating focal point of the Paris Olympics, home to the athletes' village, the Stade de France national stadium and a new 5,000-seat aquatics centre.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Games' organisers\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"a pulsating focal point\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ms Fofana echoed the sentiment of some in the area who complained that Paris 2024 did too little to help them enjoy the Games first hand.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.959486562020256e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ms Fofana\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"the sentiment\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games first hand\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We thought they would plan things for us because, well, it's the Games, it's the biggest event in the world,\\\" Ms Fofana said.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest event\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Fofana\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her flat's balcony overlooks the entrance to the Olympic village, her middle school nestled among the buildings.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her flat's balcony\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"the entrance\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"the buildings\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr David Lebon, a senior official in the Saint-Denis town hall said all students from Ms Fofana's middle school had received an invitation to a sporting event, and she and her friends took part in the torch relay.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Leb\\u00f3n\", \"score\": 0.9999939563854969, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lebon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Leb\\u00f3n\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Leb\\u00f3n\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a senior official\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"the Saint-Denis town hall\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"all students\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Fofana's middle school\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"an invitation\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"a sporting event\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"her friends\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch relay\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her mother, Ms Ketty Choux-Fofana, said she never saw the invite.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her mother\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Ketty Choux-Fofana\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"the invite\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added there had been joyful moments during the Games but cited inconveniences too: longer work commutes because of snarled local roads, heightened police checks and athletes partying under their windows as the Games wound up.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"joyful moments\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"inconveniences\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"longer work commutes\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"snarled local roads\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"police checks\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"their windows\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another Saint-Denis resident, Ms Betty Bonheur, expressed disappointment that tickets were unaffordable to many residents in Seine-Saint-Denis, the poorest of mainland France's administrative departments where the unemployment rate is nearly 50 per cent higher than the national average.\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2135, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_Suarez\", \"score\": 0.9000780451880667, \"rank\": 0.07790055995472447, \"text\": \"Betty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_Suarez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_Suarez\"}, {\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997214369068788, \"rank\": 0.0002782641944682141, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another Saint-Denis resident\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"many residents\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"the unemployment rate\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"the national average\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would have liked them to say 'Here, we have got tickets, we can give you some', to get people involved, to allocate cheaper tickets.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"cheaper tickets\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That wasn't the case,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Saint-Denis town hall spokesperson said a total of 10,000 opening ceremony invites and 9,000 invites for sports events at the Olympics and Paralympics had been offered to the town's 114,000 people.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A Saint-Denis town hall spokesperson\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"10,000 opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"sports events\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2681}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2697}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"the town's 114,000 people\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Amine Ben Dziri said his daughter was among those fortunate to receive a ticket.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Amine Ben Dziri\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2780}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She triumphed in a school competition and won a ticket to the athletics.\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a school competition\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2883}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2900}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletics\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was her first time in such a big stadium.\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her first time\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"such a big stadium\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was very nice,\\\" he told Reuters in a local park that had been transformed into a free-to-enter fan zone that was half-full.\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 3092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2993, \"end\": 3000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.737490948447508e-14, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a local park\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"a free-to-enter fan zone\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games have delighted vast, jubilant crowds with sporting events held among some of the capital's most famous landmarks including the Place de la Concorde, Eiffel Tower and Grand Palais - the picture-perfect version of Paris that can seem distant from the hard-knock streets of Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3316, \"end\": 3321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0243131133850608e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbp