es will leave behind are located in Seine-Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3693, \"end\": 3710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the three new developments\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3649}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But some residents told Reuters they questioned the sustainability of wider economic benefits.\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3737, \"end\": 3744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.737490948447508e-14, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some residents\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3731}, {\"ngram\": \"the sustainability\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3779}, {\"ngram\": \"wider economic benefits\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Mohammed Ydriss Smaali, 21, said he felt the government and local authorities had missed an opportunity to develop job prospects in the area.\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Mohammed Ydriss Smaali\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3834}, {\"ngram\": \"the government and local authorities\", \"from\": 3853, \"to\": 3889}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3915}, {\"ngram\": \"job prospects\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3940}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lots of jobs have been created, even if it was only in the short term,\\\" said Mr Smaali.\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 4043, \"entiti